OL,3,CRHI scheme closure Bill ends 'darkest
OL,4,Cepisode' in devolution in Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,FThe passing of a Stormont Bill to
OL,8,Fformally close a botched green energy
OL,9,Fscheme in Northern Ireland has been
OL,10,Fwelcomed across the Assembly chamber.
OL,12,FThe RHI (Closure of Non-Domestic
OL,13,FScheme) Bill reached its final stage
OL,14,Fon Tuesday, and is now awaiting royal
OL,15,Fassent.
OL,17,FIt provides the legal framework for
OL,18,Fclosure, with detailed operational
OL,19,Farrangements to follow in the closure
OL,20,Fregulations, subject to approval by
OL,21,Fthe Assembly.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
