OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778681475
OL,3,CRHI scheme closure Bill ends 'darkest
OL,4,Cepisode' in devolution in Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,FEconomy Minister Caoimhe Archibald
OL,8,Fhailed a consensus for the first time
OL,9,Fbetween political parties, scheme
OL,10,Fparticipants and the Treasury on how
OL,11,Fto manage it.
OL,13,FWhat is the RHI scheme?
OL,15,FThe RHI scheme, set up in Northern
OL,16,FIreland in 2012, incentivised
OL,17,Fbusinesses and farmers to switch to
OL,18,Feco-friendly boilers by paying them a
OL,19,Fsubsidy for the wood pellet fuel
OL,20,Fneeded to run them.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778681475
OL,3,CRHI scheme closure Bill ends 'darkest
OL,4,Cepisode' in devolution in Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,FBut mistakes in its designs meant the
OL,8,Fsubsidy rates were set higher than the
OL,9,Factual cost of the wood pellets, and
OL,10,Fapplicants found themselves able to
OL,11,F"burn to earn".
OL,13,FThe scandal contributed to the
OL,14,Fcollapse of devolved government in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland in January 2017, when
OL,16,Fformer deputy first minister Martin
OL,17,FMcGuinness took issue with the DUP's
OL,18,Fhandling of the scheme.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778681475
OL,3,CRHI scheme closure Bill ends 'darkest
OL,4,Cepisode' in devolution in Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,FWith Stormont facing an overspend bill
OL,8,Fof hundreds of millions of pounds,
OL,9,Fcost-control steps were taken in 2019.
OL,11,FThe New Decade, New Approach
OL,12,Fagreement, which restored the Stormont
OL,13,Finstitutions in 2020, included a
OL,14,Fcommitment that RHI would be closed
OL,15,Fdown and replaced by another scheme to
OL,16,Freduce carbon emissions.
OL,18,FThe same year, a public inquiry
OL,19,Fidentified a multiplicity of mistakes
OL,20,Fin the running of the RHI scheme.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778681475
OL,3,CRHI scheme closure Bill ends 'darkest
OL,4,Cepisode' in devolution in Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,F'It became synonymous with waste, with
OL,8,Fscandal and public anger'
OL,10,FSpeaking in the Assembly on Tuesday,
OL,11,FMs Archibald said she is confident
OL,12,Fthat the proposals for closure and
OL,13,Farrangements for existing participants
OL,14,Fwill enable the scheme to be closed in
OL,15,Fa way that is fair to both
OL,16,Fparticipants and the rate payer.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778681475
OL,3,CRHI scheme closure Bill ends 'darkest
OL,4,Cepisode' in devolution in Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,F"This Bill is vital as it lays the
OL,8,Ffoundation for the closure of the
OL,9,Fscheme, reiterates the department's
OL,10,Fcommitment to ensuring that this is
OL,11,Fachieved in a way that is fair to the
OL,12,Fparticipants and to the wider
OL,13,Ftaxpayers," she said.
OL,15,FStormont Economy Committee chairman
OL,16,Fand DUP MLA Phillip Brett commended
OL,17,Fthe reaching of a consensus, as well
OL,18,Fas the proposals for the scheme's
OL,19,Fclosure.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778681475
OL,3,CRHI scheme closure Bill ends 'darkest
OL,4,Cepisode' in devolution in Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,FSDLP MLA Sinead McLaughlin welcomed
OL,8,Fwhat she termed the "closing chapter
OL,9,Fof the darkest episodes in the history
OL,10,Fof devolution".
OL,12,F"The Renewable Heat Incentive Scheme
OL,13,Fshould have been an opportunity. It
OL,14,Fshould have helped Northern Ireland
OL,15,Ftransition towards cleaner energy and
OL,16,Fsupported businesses to reduce costs
OL,17,Fand emissions, instead, it became
OL,18,Fsynonymous with waste, with scandal
OL,19,Fand with public anger," she said.
OL,26,@pD@UOUrD@NO]tD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778681475
OL,3,CRHI scheme closure Bill ends 'darkest
OL,4,Cepisode' in devolution in Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,F"This Bill's significance is much
OL,8,Fbroader than the Bill itself, closing
OL,9,Fthe scheme finally draws a line under
OL,10,Fa policy failure that casts a long
OL,11,Fshadow across our politics and these
OL,12,Finstitutions."
OL,14,FMs McLaughlin added that huge
OL,15,Fchallenges around energy policy
OL,16,Faffordability and decarbonisation
OL,17,Fremain.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778681475
OL,3,CRHI scheme closure Bill ends 'darkest
OL,4,Cepisode' in devolution in Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,F"We need to expand renewable
OL,8,Fgeneration, we need to improve energy
OL,9,Fsecurity, we need to lower costs for
OL,10,Fhouseholds, for businesses that remain
OL,11,Fexposed to volatile political and
OL,12,Fglobal markets, but we can only do
OL,13,Fthat if there is public confidence in
OL,14,Fthe decisions that we make here," she
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778681475
OL,3,CRHI scheme closure Bill ends 'darkest
OL,4,Cepisode' in devolution in Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,F"That means transparency, that means
OL,8,Fprofit scrutiny, and that means
OL,9,Faccountability, and it means getting
OL,10,Fpolicy right from the very beginning,
OL,11,Fand the public expect better from us
OL,12,Fafter RHI."
OL,14,FAlliance MLA David Honeyford also
OL,15,Fwelcomed the Bill, describing RHI as
OL,16,Fan "episode that will live long in the
OL,17,Fmemory of this place, but something we
OL,18,Fcan now put to bed".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@KO]xD@DOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778681475
OL,3,CRHI scheme closure Bill ends 'darkest
OL,4,Cepisode' in devolution in Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,F"I do also want to acknowledge that
OL,8,Fthe minister has managed to bring all
OL,9,Fparties together here to bring this to
OL,10,Fclosure, and that's something to thank
OL,11,Fyou for and to be welcomed," he said.
OL,13,F"But the ghost of RHI cannot hold the
OL,14,Fdepartment back as we move forward. We
OL,15,Fhave got to move forward now to be
OL,16,Fable to transition away from fossil
OL,17,Ffuels and on to renewables."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@\O]uD@AOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
