CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778681475
OL,3,CRHI scheme closure Bill ends 'darkest
OL,4,Cepisode' in devolution in Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,FUUP MLA Diana Armstrong welcomed a
OL,8,Fresolution to the RHI scheme, and
OL,9,Fcalled for a way forward in terms of
OL,10,Frenewable energy.
OL,12,F"Northern Ireland urgently needs a
OL,13,Fcredible renewable energy policy
OL,14,Fframework that matches the scale of
OL,15,Fglobal competition," she said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778681475
OL,3,CRHI scheme closure Bill ends 'darkest
OL,4,Cepisode' in devolution in Northern
OL,5,CIreland
OL,7,F"Investors are already looking to
OL,8,Fjurisdictions with clear pathways for
OL,9,Fgrid capacity expansion, offshore wind
OL,10,Fdeployment and long-term renewable
OL,11,Fintegration. If we do not act quickly,
OL,12,Fthose investors will go elsewhere.
OL,14,F"We need a grid capable of supporting
OL,15,Flarge-scale renewable generation and a
OL,16,Fplanning system aligned with our
OL,17,Fenergy ambitions, and we need an
OL,18,Foffshore policy that signals to the
OL,19,Fmarket that Northern Ireland is
OL,20,Fserious about becoming a leader, not a
OL,21,Fslow adopter, in clean energy."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU}D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/14
